## Warm Up

Warm Up:run 1/4 mile   OR row 250m OR bike 2 miles.
3 rounds of 10: 10 squats, 10 sit ups, 10 double unders (or 50 single unders) and 10 push ups.

## WOD

WOD 98

### Étudiant

50 burpees for time.

### Avancée

75 burpees for time.

### Traceur

100 burpees for time.

